SUMMARY:Noontime Cornhole - North Jersey
DESCRIPTION:North Jersey Bowling\, Volleyball\, Tennis And More (BVT)\nThi
 s is an event for two to three hours of casual cornhole at a local park.\n
 \nThe gathering is tentatively scheduled for Lodi Memorial Park\, behind t
 he library\, 1 Memorial Dr.\, because the area has four permanent concrete
  boards.\n\nThere is not a ton of parking\, but there is a huge lot across
  the street as part of the shopping plaza.\n\nComment below if you have yo
 ur own boards and beanbags\, or if you want to bring another yard game. A 
 volleyball court and basketball court\, as well as turf field\, are also o
 n site. If anyone knows of any other permanent cornhole setups in North Je
 rsey\, feel free to also make that suggestion. We may relocate as a result
 .\n\n\\*\\*\\* After playing\, we'll likely be heading somewhere for a dri
 nk and snack. Feel free to suggest a spot for a post-cornhole hangout. \\*
 \\*\\*\n\nThere's no fee to play and nothing else you need to do besides s
 how up. Come anytime!! All are welcome!!! We're not in a league and are no
 t here to analyze your form. We're here for people who haven't played in m
 onths\, maybe years\, and just want to occasionally play and hang out.\n\n
 The event comes to you courtesy of prior suggestions for future events and
  our group's WhatsApp chat.\n\nHope you'll join us for our first cornhole 
 event. Questions or comments? You can message Andy on Meetup\, or call/tex
 t him at 201-234-9609.\nCheck out bowling\, soccer\, volleyball\, tennis\,
  skating or one of our other activities at: [www.meetup.com/north-jersey-b
 owling-soccer-volleyball](https://www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-socc
 er-volleyball)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleybal
 l/events/313591683/
