SUMMARY:Ping Pong Party - North Jersey 
DESCRIPTION:North Jersey Bowling\, Volleyball\, Tennis And More (BVT)\nWe'
 re a group of people who will casually hit the ball around and rotate play
 ing to 10 or 15 points for two to three hours. If there's an interest\, we
  may do king of the hill\, round robin\, a small tournament or some other 
 organized game.\n\nAll are welcome!! It's just casual fun! Come anytime! W
 e're not in a league and are not here to analyze your form.\n\nWe'll be he
 ading indoors to the table tennis tables at Ready to Golf\, 3 New Bridge R
 oad in River Edge. We'll likely have pizza delivered or hang out some more
  at Coach House Diner\, 55 Rte 4 in Hackensack.\n\nReady to Golf has a lot
  to offer\, including rentable table tennis tables\, and comes as a recomm
 endation of Joe\, one of our many regulars.\n\nWe'll be reserving five or 
 six tables for singles and doubles play but we will get more if more than 
 20 people show up or they're available.\n\nThe rental price covers paddles
  and balls. Final pricing will be somewhere in the neighborhood of $10-15 
 per person. Please bring cash to pay for what you owe! We'll settle the bi
 ll before play.\n\nFor planning purposes\, we also ask that if you're stop
 ping by later than 8 p.m.\, that you please let me know by commenting belo
 w\, or calling or texting me.\n\nThere is a snack bar on site\, but it's o
 nly open until 7:30 p.m. There are some bottled drinks available and a wat
 er fountain\, but you're welcome to bring food and beverages from the outs
 ide. It's BYOB friendly. There's also plenty of seating and space for hang
 ing out on the side when not playing and some televisions with sports prog
 ramming.\n\nIf interested in learning more about the place\, here's the we
 bsite: www.readytogolf.com\n\nHope you'll join us for our sixth ping pong 
 event. Questions\, comments\, concerns or having trouble finding us? You c
 an message Andy Milone on Meetup\, or call/text him at 201-234-9609.\n\nIf
  interested\, check out one of our many other events. We do bowling\, voll
 eyball\, tennis\, soccer\, hiking\, martial arts\, billiards\, dancing and
  bar crawls: [www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleyball](https
 ://www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleyball)
